OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start in places this
OL,6,Fmorning, but the cloud will quickly
OL,7,Fburn away to leave a largely sunny day
OL,8,Fwith just a little fair weather cloud.
OL,9,FBreezy, especially over the hills but
OL,10,Ffeeling very warm once again.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine and dry evening will
OL,13,Flead to a largely clear night. Some
OL,14,Fpatchy low cloud may develop later,
OL,15,Fmainly in the east. A warm night,
OL,16,Fespecially in the cities.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
