OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAnother dry and very warm day
OL,6,Fexpected, although perhaps a little
OL,7,Fmore cloud around compared to of late.
OL,8,FWinds lighter adding to the very warm
OL,9,Ffeel.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FLargely dry and settled throughout
OL,13,Fwith plenty of sunshine. A small
OL,14,Fchance of a few thunderstorms, but
OL,15,Fmost areas will avoid them. Staying
OL,16,Fhot by day and warm by night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
